lead_paragraph: Borussia Dortmund coach Thomas Tuchel urged his club to do what they can to prevent Pierre-Emerick Aubameyang from leaving, though he understood the prolific striker's ultimate wish was to play for Real Madrid.

headline.print_headline: Aubameyang Vital to Dortmund, Though Real Dream Is Normal - Tuchel
headline.main: Aubameyang Vital to Dortmund, Though Real Dream Is Normal - Tuchel
